            <div style="font-size:40px;margin-bottom:12px;">${u.icon}</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;
                        color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:10px;">${u.name}</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#8892a4;line-height:1.6;">${u.desc}</div>
          </div>`).join('')}
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#3a4456;font-style:italic;">
        Your other abilities are unchanged. This upgrade is saved to your character permanently.
      </div>
    </div>`;
